"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806305","HM Treasury","false","2017-12-21","<p>11 data incidents were recorded in 2015-16 and 10 were recorded in 2016-17. None of the incidents involved personal data and none were reported to the Information Commissioner's Office.</p><p> </p><p>HM Treasury take security breaches very seriously. In every case where a breach is recorded, the scale of the breach is determined by assessing the circumstances of each case in line with our department’s disciplinary guidance. In cases where there is clear evidence of misconduct, this will result in disciplinary measures.</p>","Harrogate and Knaresborough","Andrew Jones",,"2017-12-21T13:16:31.887Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806305/answer","Biography information for Andrew Jones","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806305/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806305/answer",,,,,"14","Treasury","CaTreasury","2017-12-13","Treasury: Data Protection","1","House of Commons","To ask Mr Chancellor of the Exchequer, how many data incidents his Department (a) recorded and (b) reported to the Information Commissioner's Office in (i) 2015-16 and (ii) 2016-17.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","119497"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806306","Department for International Trade","false","2017-12-19","<p>The post of Senior Information Risk Officer has not been vacant since the Department was formed in 2016.</p>","Chelsea and Fulham","Greg Hands",,"2017-12-19T13:53:24.407Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806306/answer","Biography information for Greg Hands","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806306/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806306/answer",,,,,"202","International Trade","International Trade","2017-12-13","Department for International Trade: Data Protection","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for International Trade, how many times his Department's Senior Information Risk Officer role has been vacant for a week or longer since 2012.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","119498"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806307","Ministry of Justice","false","2017-12-20","<p>Departments are obligated to publish breaches of personal data in their Annual Reports and Accounts. Copies of the Ministry of Justice’s Annual Report and Accounts, including 2015-16 and 2016-17 and can be found here:</p><p> </p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/630239/moj-annual-report-2016-17.pdf" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/attachment_data/file/630239/moj-annual-report-2016-17.pdf</a> (pages 34-35)</p><p> </p><p><a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/ministry-of-justice-annual-report-and-accounts-2015-to-2016" target="_blank">https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/ministry-of-justice-annual-report-and-accounts-2015-to-2016</a> (page 32)</p><p> </p><p>The Ministry of Justice takes any data loss seriously. The Department handles millions of records of personal data and each loss is assessed, including instances of small localised losses, which make up the vast majority of the incidents which occur. The department continues to take steps to address the number of data incidents occurring including staff training and awareness campaigns and a review of the governance structures in place to protect data and information.</p><p> </p><p>In compliance with the requirements of the Cabinet Office Security Policy Framework the Department has had four departmental Senior Information Risk Owners in post since 2012 and there have been no vacancies during that period.</p>","Bracknell","Dr Phillip Lee","119478","2017-12-20T11:16:33.08Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806307/answer","Biography information for Dr Phillip Lee","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806307/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806307/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2017-12-13","Ministry of Justice: Data Protection","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, how many times his Department's Senior Information Risk Officer role has been vacant for a week or longer since 2012.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","119499"
