"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806310","Scotland Office","false","2017-12-20","<p>Since 2012, the role has been vacant, on one occasion, for longer than a week. This was due to a gap between Senior Civil Servant appointments, when the Senior Information Risk Officer role was vacant. During this period, Senior Information Risk Officer responsibilities were undertaken by the Department’s Data Protection Officer.</p>","Dumfriesshire, Clydesdale and Tweeddale","David Mundell",,"2017-12-20T11:22:12.297Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806310/answer","Biography information for David Mundell","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806310/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/806310/answer",,,,,"2","Scotland","Scotland","2017-12-13","Scotland Office: Data Protection","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Scotland, how many times his Department's Senior Information Risk Officer role has been vacant for a week or longer since 2012.","false","Biography information for Jon Trickett","Hemsworth","Jon Trickett","119502"
